<plot>An author (Randall Slavin) suffering writer's block has to face his own demons when his best friend (David Hayter) shows up with a completed manuscript, a publishing deal, and the publisher's daughter (Andrea Roth) in tow. In his frustration, he proceeds to pound out a story in which he kills the best friend. Metaphorically, as he gains confidence, he does destroy the friend's egotistical confidence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087115</url></doc>
